        "content": "<p class=\"tw-intro\" style=\"color:#78716c;font-size:.88rem;font-style:italic;margin-bottom:.5rem;border-left:3px solid #c0956c;padding-left:.6rem\">紮實的學理基礎是您臨床與國考成功的基石，本節鼓勵您深入研讀這些文獻，建立更全面的知識體系。</p><p class=\"tw-intro\" style=\"color:#78716c;font-size:.88rem;font-style:italic;margin-bottom:.5rem;border-left:3px solid #c0956c;padding-left:.6rem\">紮實的學理基礎是臨床與國考成功的關鍵。本節列出重要參考文獻，鼓勵您深入研讀，建立更全面的知識體系。</p><h3>參考文獻與資料來源</h3>\n<h3>5. 參考文獻與資料來源（部分重點）</h3>\n<ul class=\"n\"><li><strong>Oral and Maxillofacial Pathology, 4th Edition</strong></li><li><strong>Gnepp&#x27;s Diagnostic Surgical Pathology of the Head and Neck, 3rd Edition</strong></li><li><strong>White and Pharoah&#x27;s Oral Radiology - Principles and Interpretation, 8th Edition</strong></li><li><strong>Oral and Maxillofacial Pathology: A Rationale for Diagnosis and Treatment, 2nd Edition</strong></li><li><strong>Dentomaxillofacial Radiology</strong> 相關論文與系統回顧（2010-2016）</li><li>牙源性腫瘤與囊腫系統回顧：Ameloblastic fibroma, Calcifying epithelial odontogenic tumor等</li><li>臨床與放射診斷指引：Jaw lesions associated with impacted tooth</li></ul>\n<hr>\n<hr>\n<h3>11. 參考文獻與資料來源整理</h3>\n<div class=\"pearl\">本講義資料整合多本權威口腔及頭頸部病理學、放射學書籍與多篇系統性文獻回顧，詳盡涵蓋牙源性囊腫、腫瘤及相關顎骨病變之臨床與放射診斷。</div>\n<hr>\n<p>以上為本段講義內容完整整理，涵蓋牙源性囊腫與腫瘤與阻生齒相關性、影像表現、生長特性及診斷要點，適用於日後複習與考試準備。</p>"
